title: Superman Batman (1-54 + Annuals)
description:
Superman/Batman is an update of the previous series World's Finest Comics, in which Superman and Batman regularly joined forces. The series explores the camaraderie, antagonism, and friendship between the two characters. Jeph Loeb, the series' first writer, introduced a dual-narrator technique to present the characters' often opposing viewpoints and estimations of each other, which subsequent series writers have maintained. Most of the storylines are independent and self-contained from the ongoing or crossover storylines in the other Batman and Superman titles.
